            <a href="https://github.com/orgs/satisfactory-factories/projects/2/views/1?filterQuery=+milestone%3A%22Alpha+4%22+&sortedBy%5Bdirection%5D=asc&sortedBy%5BcolumnId%5D=Title" style="color: var(--link-color);">Click here</a> for an itemised list of changes on GitHub!
